/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1b90f4071c9bc5f36cf48243e65efe51caeb22","tid":389171,"uid":51021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:27:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>農米莊 個湯好飲 推介椰子雞同喇沙</blockquote><br />\n垃圾</blockquote><br />\n難食都比個理由架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9f39308009f466f43f8708bb1e343b02fb8ae5","tid":389171,"uid":142522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:50:26.000Z","msg":"葵涌間小鍋米線😍"},{"pid":"cf4fcf89873897b547c9f91279bf51df63ed541e","tid":389171,"uid":141706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>觀塘 黑山羊米線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚穌啲肉"},{"pid":"19fee6304d24016ac86fd866c927c85aa32d2c51","tid":389171,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:36:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">屯門新墟開左間餐廳</span>有米線食<br />\n嗌酸辣有新鮮肉碎  個湯夠酸好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其次就係屯門雲貴風  雲味園<br />\n不過雲味園好撚串  我都好少去食</blockquote><br />\n邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不吃不可隔離<br />\n叫巴打廳<br />\n上次唔知睇咩post見到有巴打推介就試<br />\n上左癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n番工lunch成日食 就係無食佢啲米線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屯門雲貴風開左元朗分店<br />\n廚師成日過撚左去 而家屯門好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又污漕<br />\n以前就真係日日屌都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣唯一雲貴川<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係我覺得新墟個間既米線同雲貴風似先鐘意食"},{"pid":"0a77a7fc1ea1059d4e4added652e770ec4ad51a3","tid":389171,"uid":126919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:56:11.000Z","msg":"太子 貴香園"},{"pid":"4fa149f5d2658e2af50fa05add61a04078e32907","tid":389171,"uid":35063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:05:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>荃灣唯一雲貴川<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前還好，而家愈黎愈油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係貪佢夠油夠香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef1582a812d378d106ec629fb88fe4177079c30","tid":389171,"uid":75072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:07:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長沙環雲南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個湯無得輸</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374fd14bb21f3bfc0107bd2f477de2515d287943","tid":389171,"uid":12414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:10:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新蒲崗雲南人家 豆腐花米線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c5014e19e918ef41469a922dec29485de91243","tid":389171,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"三酸 砂砂湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74ceeac6830ccc7a4b1c860738f63d72f98c480","tid":389171,"uid":9544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T19:33:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>農米莊 個湯好飲 推介椰子雞同喇沙</blockquote><br />\n垃圾</blockquote><br />\n難食都比個理由架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我食麻辣<br />\n佢好明顯係清湯再加幾羹辣油就算<br />\n唔係辣湯 <br />\n完全飲到清湯還清湯 辣油還辣油<br />\n<br />\n我男朋友食芫茜湯<br />\n又係清湯加芫茜蓉就算<br />\n好心你都落下鹽 煲一煲等個味岀d呀<br />\n<br />\n雞係幾嫩滑 但冇雞味<br />\n<br />\n食過一次真係想當面教下老闆點煮靚湯底"},{"pid":"cf1b6c39faa9fa046f0efca8f8b3fb9675c9a1bf","tid":389171,"uid":42900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>觀塘 阿老表</blockquote><br />\n識貨，以為香港d人食開屎添，譚仔都可以話好食，服</blockquote><br />\n麻麻地，叫左帶皮羊肉，肉有啲(鞋)"},{"pid":"dde8704fb571f8980a28300473e550132778e460","tid":389171,"uid":53180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太子 川之味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食足4年"},{"pid":"8c05174c9d8df444bc4bcb67afe2c6bbfc522aad","tid":389171,"uid":51021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:30:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>農米莊 個湯好飲 推介椰子雞同喇沙</blockquote><br />\n垃圾</blockquote><br />\n難食都比個理由架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我食麻辣<br />\n佢好明顯係清湯再加幾羹辣油就算<br />\n唔係辣湯 <br />\n完全飲到清湯還清湯 辣油還辣油<br />\n<br />\n我男朋友食芫茜湯<br />\n又係清湯加芫茜蓉就算<br />\n好心你都落下鹽 煲一煲等個味岀d呀<br />\n<br />\n雞係幾嫩滑 但冇雞味<br />\n<br />\n食過一次真係想當面教下老闆點煮靚湯底</blockquote><br />\n我食椰子雞同喇沙 個湯好好味喎其他配料就中等 係唯一豬頸肉好好食"},{"pid":"ec1ed0ca6f06a03462384be53c63bf87eee84fd7","tid":389171,"uid":134864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"我個名"},{"pid":"9bc9a41b0d31c9143698a64d078af97cb87b96c6","tid":389171,"uid":133980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:32:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屯門 雲川燒 <br />\n燒豬頸肉好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb11ed7cc1795e37eccd0169e71d1a1957f4fc1","tid":389171,"uid":61578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長沙環雲南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個湯無得輸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n青山道果邊果間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d3ae8a1b967bee8372cbe11d5c28beab26e549","tid":389171,"uid":137055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:37:07.000Z","msg":"譚仔係劣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84928963d25c9f47c80d7c8161fcdc1bee674794","tid":389171,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:48:55.000Z","msg":"呢啲post都係睇狗也不屌同垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會選到"},{"pid":"8fb872168fcb16f50836bc61599d62ebc5073036","tid":389171,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲post都係睇狗也不屌同垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會選到</blockquote><br />\n有乜建議?"},{"pid":"18b73fab347594e7e280ccb4870d12c8d7b0aa04","tid":389171,"uid":45195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:00:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酸辣"},{"pid":"c3bc40450282cb75136ff76e27f193491f385819","tid":389171,"uid":35517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:01:54.000Z","msg":"三哥, 雲桂香, 麻辣川<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a69e8148861810424b0cf79dd4802be5219cdac","tid":389171,"uid":35517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定係南記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南記反而覺得麻麻, 啲味唔夠濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7ce7722f200ee0c402f40acabba48dee14b73b","tid":389171,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:37:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢啲post都係睇狗也不屌同垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會選到</blockquote><br />\n有乜建議?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorrry我意思係講邊間都比人話狗也不屌同垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己唔係好食米線 長沙灣麻辣川我都ok<br />\n啲朋友就好鍾意唯一雲貴川同石蔭(石籬?)米線 <br />\n老闆娘都有啲擁躉 佢地鍾意食啲餸 雞球呀春卷"},{"pid":"b7fd656e94033fdb4428c3ac74a2f11a3033a75b","tid":389171,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:42:05.000Z","msg":"三gor屌打all"},{"pid":"1aa0201843f5888855127ea5e2269f4173c8e929","tid":389171,"uid":1671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:11:16.000Z","msg":"貴川<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沙嗲湯底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12dd3c73b1c3a5cf2f85a2b5168f640f3eaf2a65","tid":389171,"uid":21055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"