 /></blockquote><br />\n千色果邊果間執左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5376b8558fde4939328dcb38c2b65a1aa89c07b","tid":389171,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想試老闆娘，但都幾遠下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋要睇實佢fb 成日唔開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過有一次專登去，佢無開<br />\n同埋一日好像開幾粒鐘"},{"pid":"75502f70606fcba95745663964260260b600e8ea","tid":389171,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:04:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一定係南記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南記反而覺得麻麻, 啲味唔夠濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南記要落佢個辣醬，好撚香"},{"pid":"3cf3d971b3f4e31afc5ddc67478062e8bb3000f4","tid":389171,"uid":142653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:05:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"823743ede106f6ad8617bee1f317c8a3590705a5","tid":389171,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:21:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想試老闆娘，但都幾遠下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋要睇實佢fb 成日唔開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過有一次專登去，佢無開<br />\n同埋一日好像開幾粒鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 我有一次睇佢fb話開 去到又話準備唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣中學時代 要打過去問有無開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abcca7d4a2448c295a2a20ad183901a986a3db25","tid":389171,"uid":35749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>觀塘 阿老表</blockquote><br />\n識貨，以為香港d人食開屎添，譚仔都可以話好食，服</blockquote><br />\n麻麻地，叫左帶皮羊肉，肉有啲(鞋)</blockquote><br />\n啲羊有臭味 係唔新鮮嗰啲肉臭 有好多都係得皮冇肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6b5ec40f75f6a4f688e827ebfce384b37fa8bd","tid":389171,"uid":124756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>觀塘 阿老表</blockquote><br />\n識貨，以為香港d人食開屎添，譚仔都可以話好食，服</blockquote><br />\n係咪講緊個間雲南黑山羊老表唔知咩米線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524c73e947b332728eb519ecfbbdbded11033d0c","tid":389171,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T18:43:08.000Z","msg":"荃灣間唯一咸到 識食一定兆和街肥仔米線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e1bd9681450490aa3751e1d967e03d4201bc37","tid":389171,"uid":104434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T19:26:49.000Z","msg":"金西南！"},{"pid":"12746779a3f4d42975951cafa4954772e489a941","tid":389171,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T19:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e3ec6f1176ccffa473900bc515a9cbad25bdfc","tid":389171,"uid":81053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T20:16:31.000Z","msg":"金西南<br />\n雲南桂林"},{"pid":"65f4ae84a201dd4bf593a1242cdffe01b6234e58","tid":389171,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T00:05:01.000Z","msg":"太子川之味"},{"pid":"634054ebdd1394caac2acf5084cfde6396272ef4","tid":389171,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣新富盈<br />\n係另一個層次嘅事"},{"pid":"b2779e4a77f334d8800293b3f0fe8b9c9bd9bc7b","tid":389171,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T04:57:10.000Z","msg":"老闆娘"},{"pid":"0e9a9336b751fa6a190f232f30a1df813cae836a","tid":389171,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T04:58:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嫲孫樂<br />\n好少試新鋪頭，好多鋪頭啲麻辣一啲麻口嘅感覺都冇得個辣字，呢間起碼叫做真係有麻痺感<br />\n不過好似好多巴打覺得唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你食開屎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢間d 野咩味都無<br />\n是但一間譚仔南記雲桂香都屌打佢</blockquote><br />\n麻辣冇麻好食得去邊呀又<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23da03cb81936b82f4846527c57c4d6e7f90dfd5","tid":389171,"uid":112920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新蒲江Mikiki正門對面<br />\n滇二哥雲南小鍋米線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全港最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前去開隔幾條街以外果間一品滇,<br />\n自從一品滇執左先發現滇二哥,呢兩間野既米線同湯真係好似,係第到真係搵唔到咁正咁濃又多肉碎既湯<br />\n不過小食就差好遠,要乜冇乜<br />\n不過最最最似既係杯奶茶,難飲到仆街"},{"pid":"6a0b65c65451eedf18a1aa2535da2db5522da88d","tid":389171,"uid":92195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:33:42.000Z","msg":"荃灣雲南過橋米線"},{"pid":"9207c4231caa52386d4d4a5fd499084d69464883","tid":389171,"uid":7432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:38:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小妹第一次係飲食台開po 新黎新豬肉 有怪莫怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人認為旺角豉油街嗰間貴村最好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 熱伴同酸辣都好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無其他推介 就黎飛 好想食碗好食嘅米線先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貴川？間嘢係幾好味 不過食完要飲2L水"},{"pid":"2176d3d82a316e9076a4a8355c164a982c506822","tid":389171,"uid":54965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屯門 雲川燒 <br />\n燒豬頸肉好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img sr